::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer frowns, looking at Vamprah as she goes into stasis lock 
from another discharge of energy. Glancing at his scanners, he sees 
that the energy is coming from her necklace.

"Looks like th' necklace's doin' it," he says, reaching down to try 
and take the necklace off of Vamprah.
